Package: OAPRS
Type: Package
Title: Sample overlap in Polygenic Risk Score
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: Seokho Jeong <seokho92@snu.ac.kr>
Description: OAPRS is designed to help and guide adjusting sample overlap bias in building PRS without overfitting.
    OAPRS consists of four main steps. Summary information preparation, Sample overlap adjustment, PRS construction, and validation using visual diagnostics.
